Iga '''Asif n Burgrag''' yan wasif illan ɣ tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]]. Tiɣzi nns tlkm 240 km.

Aɣbalu nns iga-tt idrarn n [[Aṭlas anammas|Waṭlas anammas]] ɣ yat tuttuyt n 1 627 m ɣ ammas n yan udrar iga s yism [[Adrar n Mturzgan]] (ɣ tmnadt n Xmissat) d Gru (ɣ tmnadt n Xnifra), d ar itffi ɣ [[Ill Aṭlasi|yill Aṭlasi]] gr tamdint n [[Sla]] d tamaẓunt n tmazirt [[Rrbaṭ|Rrbat]].

